msgid "Run nginx -t to test configuration before reloading. Prevents invalid config from breaking the server."
msgstr "重载前运行 nginx -t 测试配置，防止无效配置导致服务中断。"

msgid "Changes saved but not applied because dangerous edit mode is enabled. Disable it to apply changes."
msgstr "更改已保存但未应用，因为危险编辑模式已启用。请禁用后再应用更改。"

msgid "HSTS Max-Age"
msgstr "HSTS Max-Age"

